ENTRY            A0850   20260205   20260401   20260401       A131
SUBENT        A0850001   20260205   20260401   20260401       A131
BIB                  7         17
TITLE      Study of the 2n-evaporation channel in the
            4,6He + 206,208Pb reactions
AUTHOR     (S.M.Lukyanov, Yu.E.Penionzhkevich, R.A.Astabatian,
            N.A.Demekhina, Z.Dlouhy, M.P.Ivanov, R.Kalpakchieva,
            A.A.Kulko, E.R.Markarian, V.A.Maslov, R.V.Revenko,
            N.K.Skobelev, V.I.Smirnov, Yu.G.Sobolev, W.Trazska,
            S.V.Khlebnikov)
REFERENCE  (J,PL/B,670,321,2009) Final publication
           (J,PAN,72,1617,2009) Engl.Trans.of Yad.Fiz.72(2009)1674
           (J,YF,72,1674,2009)
           (J,JP/CS,420,012068,2013) 208Pb(a,2n)210Po data in fig.
INSTITUTE  (4ZZZDUB,3CZRUJF,2SF JYV,4RUSRI)
METHOD     (STTA,ACTIV)
DECAY-DATA (84-PO-210,138.D,A,5300.)
HISTORY    (20100402C) SB
           (20140226U) REFERENCE: JP/CS added; PAN: p1611 -> p1617
           (20260205U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              17
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           20
SUBENT        A0850002   20260205   20260401   20260401       A131
BIB                 10         28
REACTION   (82-PB-206(2-HE-6,2N)84-PO-210,,SIG)
FACILITY   (CYCLO,4ZZZDUB) U-400M cyclotron of FLNR and
           separator ACCULINNA.
MONITOR    (82-PB-206(2-HE-6,EL)82-PB-206,,DA)
DETECTOR   (MAGSP) Magnetic spectrometer MSP-144
SAMPLE     The stack consisted of several targets (10 to 14) made
           of the enriched Pb-206 material with Al degraders
           inserted between them.
           These Al degraders with thickness 5 to 20 um were
           necessary to gradually decrease the beam energy on
           each Pb target.
           The targets were prepared by deposition of the Pb
           sulphide on Ti-backings 4 um thick.
COMMENT    By authors: Two methods of beam monochromatization
           were used in the experiment.
           By S.Lukyanov (2014-01-21):
             S.M. Lukyanov et al., Phys.Lett.B670(2009)321 gives
            the final data set.
REL-REF    (N,F0837008,Yu.E.Penionzhkevich+,J,EPJ/A,31,185,2007)
            Preliminary data to be superseded by A0850.002
           (N,O1413002,Yu.E.Penionzhkevich+,J,PRL,96,162701,2006)
            Preliminary data to be superseded by A0850.002
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information on source of uncertainties
STATUS     (TABLE,,S.M.Lukyanov+,J,PL/B,670,321,2009) Received by
